{"tid":910843,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【下月就爭子女撫養權】畢彼特為代言首度訪京 與吳彥祖台上玩Selfie心情靚","createTime":"2018-11-21T12:45:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T05:21:50.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2c87147f99f7411775cf54cbbefa3c77acd92706","tid":910843,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T12:45:21.000Z","msg":"荷李活型佬畢彼特（Brad Pitt）近日雖然忙於與安琪蓮娜祖莉（Angelina Jolie）搞離婚，及準備下月與安琪蓮娜對簿公堂爭子女撫養權（新聞連結： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2RBSnyO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2RBSnyO&d=sg4kdzOBGnbgirfSeSyDw5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=6f31b87f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2RBSnyO</a> ），不過佢噚日飛咗去北京，出席代言手錶嘅活動，會上仲有近年忙於拍美劇嘅華裔男神吳彥祖。<br />\n原來今次係畢彼特首度訪京，見佢全程勁好笑容，又喺台上與吳彥祖等嘉賓玩selfie，睇嚟心情未受婚及子女撫養權官司影響。<br />\n畢彼特同吳彥祖都喺會上大賣口乖，盛讚代言手錶靚，而吳彥祖仲話自己第一隻錶就係代言品牌嘅產品，今次收到代言邀請，喺得知同畢彼特及查理絲泰朗（Charlize Theron）等同為代言人前，一早已經揸定主意加入成為一份子。<br />\n而吳彥祖心情亦都非常好，佢噚晚同今日都分別喺自己個Instagram度貼噚晚活動啲相出嚟，睇番佢啲留言，睇嚟佢都好滿意自己一身打扮。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181121/large/1542798762_ffb2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181121%2Flarge%2F1542798762_ffb2.jpg&h=7278e00a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181121/large/1542798762_e525.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181121%2Flarge%2F1542798762_e525.jpg&h=c12ef32f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181121/large/1542798762_eeb8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181121%2Flarge%2F1542798762_eeb8.jpg&h=916d21c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181121/large/1542798766_5cca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181121%2Flarge%2F1542798766_5cca.jpg&h=79661a9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181121/large/1542798766_dcdd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181121%2Flarge%2F1542798766_dcdd.jpg&h=ecd77bd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181121/large/1542798766_9f16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181121%2Flarge%2F1542798766_9f16.jpg&h=9612d037&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181121/58941474\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181121%2F58941474&d=sg4kdzOBGnbgirfSeSyDw5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=0d516efe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181121%2F58941474&h=073aa170\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181121/58941474</a>"},{"pid":"08f9e8d7828e2aa43f066fe954b51a45c92b4195","tid":910843,"uid":22633,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T12:48:59.000Z","msg":"當年金童玉女，最後都要對薄公堂<br />\n真係唏噓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82f320b6f299a7eebbc7756065136d305c2db96","tid":910843,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T17:00:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"beb367a884dae2747283d221847af1d09573e99b","tid":910843,"uid":98659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"08f9e8d7828e2aa43f066fe954b51a45c92b4195","tid":910843,"uid":22633,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T12:48:59.000Z","msg":"當年金童玉女，最後都要對薄公堂<br />\n真係唏噓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2